3e)\" throughout all component Makefiles, with a shared Makefile definition of many common commands, and start using absolute paths in those shared definitions so that we\u0027re no longer vulnerable to build failures resulting from unexpected $PATH values.\n\nAnother approach might be to try to validate $PATH as part of a general build-environment validator run early in the build, but that seems harder to do properly.\n\nIn any case, that\u0027s a bigger chunk of work than just this change, but if you\u0027d prefer me to use $(TAR) now, I\u0027m ok with that."},{"timestamp":1529711875,"reviewer":{"name":"Trent Mick","email":"trentm@gmail.com","username":"trentm"},"message":"Patch Set 2: Integration-Approval+1\n\nNope, either is fine with me for now. :)"},{"timestamp":1529944358,"reviewer":{"name":"Tim Foster","email":"tim.foster@joyent.com","username":"timfoster"},"message":"Uploaded patch set 3: Commit message was updated."},{"timestamp":1529944391,"reviewer":{"name":"Gerrit Code Review","email":"no-reply@cr.joyent.us"},"message":"Change has been successfully merged by Tim Foster"}],"currentPatchSet":{"number":"3","revision":"296c902be839b83eec34c6da21e79578cc1ae89a","parents":["89dc917c18fc3e9739376e9eca229dedd229003e"],"ref":"refs/changes/99/4399/3","uploader":{"name":"Tim Foster","email":"tim.foster@joyent.com","username":"timfoster"},"createdOn":1529944358,"author":{"name":"Tim Foster","email":"tim.foster@joyent.com","username":"timfoster"},"isDraft":false,"kind":"NO_CODE_CHANGE","approvals":[{"type":"CI-Testing","description":"CI-Testing","value":"1","grantedOn":1529596526,"by":{"name":"Joyent Automation","username":"joyent-automation"}},{"type":"Code-Review","description":"Code-Review","value":"1","grantedOn":1529601593,"by":{"name":"Trent Mick","email":"trentm@gmail.com","username":"trentm"}},{"type":"Integration-Approval","description":"Integration-Approval","value":"1","grantedOn":1529711875,"by":{"name":"Trent Mick","email":"trentm@gmail.com","username":